name: Neha Food Products
overview:
Incorporated in the year 1990, at Delhi ( India ), we, “Neha Food Products” are a prominent processor and supplier of premium quality Biscuit Products, Bread Products and Bread Toasts. The offered product range is hygienically processed at our well equipped processing unit to ensure their longer shelf life and intact nutritious values.

Quality Assurance: As a quality conscious organization, every assortment of Biscuit Products, Bread Products and Bread Toasts are available with us of the best quality. Our experienced team of quality controllers observes each and every phase of the processing process to assure food products that are devoid of any defects and complete with respect to taste and aroma.

Infrastructural Facilities: Our organization comprises state-of-the-art infrastructural facilities and properly automated facilities which are segregated into processing facility, quality control, warehousing & packaging, cold storage and other departments.

Our Team: With the support of our highly experienced and dedicated team of professionals, we have carved a niche in the food industry. Backed by rich food industry experience, we have trained our team in the methods of processing the finest assortment of Biscuit Products, Bread Products and Bread Toasts.

Why Us ?: We hold rich expertise in processing and supplying utmost quality array of Biscuit Products, Bread Products and Bread Toasts. To provide maximum satisfaction, we are offering our wide range of products at most competitive prices. We have some key point which makes us different from competitors.
